    <p>
      When <m>a \lt 1</m>, <m>\ln(a) \lt 0</m> and so <m>\Exp{a}</m> is obtained from <m>\exp</m> by a <xref ref="def-reflection" text="title"/>  and a <xref ref="def-horizontal_scaling" text="title"/> of <m>\exp</m>.
    </p>
